; UNSAT: (x XOR y) == x + y for 12-bit x, y (only true when no carry, i.e. AND(x,y)==0)
; But we also require AND(x,y) != 0, making it UNSAT
; Domain: 4096^2 = 16M — tests multi-variable blast
; Expected: UNSAT
1 sort bitvec 12
2 sort bitvec 1
3 input 1 x
4 input 1 y
5 xor 1 3 4
6 add 1 3 4
7 eq 2 5 6
8 and 1 3 4
9 zero 1
10 neq 2 8 9
11 and 2 7 10
12 bad 11
